column5: Does anyone know where and how much?
Thanks! Apparently the winds were too strong and they weren't renting any boats. Oh well. The season has just begun!

Trust me, you didn't want to be out on Sturgeon Lake yesterday in a small boat anyway, 3' waves and we are on a somewhat sheltered part of the lake. I think it is really good of them to not let people go out when conditions are that bad.
If you need a second person to help with the costs i am in just give me a shout.
Patrick. I'm not workin right now so call me anytime.
